---
// ShorVisual.astro — Simplified explanation of Shor's factoring algorithm
---

<div class="shv-wrap">
  <h3 class="shv-title">Shor's Algorithm — Why Quantum Threatens Encryption</h3>
  <p class="shv-sub">RSA encryption relies on factoring being hard. Shor's algorithm makes it easy.</p>

  <div class="shv-compare">
    <div class="shv-column" style="--i:0">
      <div class="shv-badge shv-badge--red">RSA TODAY</div>
      <div class="shv-chain">
        <div class="shv-link">Public Key: N = p × q</div>
        <div class="shv-link shv-link--strong">Finding p and q is astronomically hard</div>
        <div class="shv-link">Classical: ~10⁸ years for 2048-bit key</div>
      </div>
      <div class="shv-verdict shv-verdict--green">✓ Safe (for now)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="shv-column" style="--i:1">
      <div class="shv-badge shv-badge--amber">WITH SHOR'S ALGORITHM</div>
      <div class="shv-chain">
        <div class="shv-link">Same problem: factor N into p × q</div>
        <div class="shv-link shv-link--weak">Quantum period-finding makes it efficient</div>
        <div class="shv-link">Quantum: hours (with enough qubits)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="shv-verdict shv-verdict--red">✗ Broken (future threat)</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <details class="shv-detail">
    <summary class="shv-sum">How does it actually work? (simplified)</summary>
    <div class="shv-body">
      <div class="shv-s"><span class="shv-n">1</span> Pick a random number</div>
      <div class="shv-s"><span class="shv-n">2</span> Use quantum superposition to find the "period" of a mathematical function related to N</div>
      <div class="shv-s"><span class="shv-n">3</span> The period reveals the factors through classical math (GCD)</div>
      <div class="shv-s"><span class="shv-n">4</span> The quantum part (Quantum Fourier Transform) is what makes step 2 exponentially faster</div>
    </div>
  </details>

  <div class="shv-note">We don't have enough stable qubits yet to break RSA-2048. But "harvest now, decrypt later" attacks are already happening — steal encrypted data today, decrypt it when quantum hardware catches up.</div>
</div>

<style>
  .shv-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .shv-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 .25rem}
  .shv-sub{color:#64748b;font-size:.78rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem;font-family:monospace}
  .shv-compare{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:1rem}
  @media(max-width:500px){.shv-compare{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .shv-column{background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem;opacity:0;animation:shvIn .5s ease forwards;animation-delay:calc(var(--i)*.2s)}
  .shv-badge{font-size:.6rem;font-family:monospace;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:.75rem}
  .shv-badge--red{color:#ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,.1);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.2)}
  .shv-badge--amber{color:#f59e0b;background:rgba(245,158,11,.1);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.2)}
  .shv-chain{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;margin-bottom:.75rem}
  .shv-link{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.68rem;font-family:monospace;padding:6px 10px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.15);border-radius:6px;border-left:2px solid #334155}
  .shv-link--strong{border-left-color:#4ade80;color:#4ade80}
  .shv-link--weak{border-left-color:#ef4444;color:#f87171}
  .shv-verdict{font-size:.68rem;font-family:monospace;font-weight:600}
  .shv-verdict--green{color:#4ade80}.shv-verdict--red{color:#ef4444}
  .shv-detail{background:rgba(0,0,0,.15);border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:1rem;overflow:hidden}
  .shv-detail[open]{border-color:#a78bfa30}
  .shv-sum{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:.75rem;padding:10px 14px;cursor:pointer;list-style:none}
  .shv-sum::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
  .shv-body{padding:0 14px 12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
  .shv-s{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;line-height:1.5}
  .shv-n{width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(167,139,250,.12);color:#a78bfa;font-size:.55rem;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-family:monospace}
  .shv-note{color:#f59e0b;font-size:.7rem;line-height:1.6;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(245,158,11,.05);border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.15)}
  @keyframes shvIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
</style>
